<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
        body {
            background: #0a0618;
            font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .header h1 { color: #8B5CF6; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 900; }
        .logout-btn {
            background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.2);
            color: #ef4444;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .card {
            background: #1a0a3e;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .card h2 { color: #8B5CF6; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .card p { color: #d4d0e0; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0; }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
            color: #10b981;
            border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.2);
        }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #3d2d5a; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🔐 UNBREAKABLE</h1>
        <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">🚪 Logout</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Welcome Back!</h2>
        <p><strong>Device ID:</strong> <span style="color:#8B5CF6;font-family:monospace;"><%= deviceId %></span></p>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> <span style="color:#8B5CF6;"><%= role %></span></p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="badge">✅ Active</span></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
        <h2>📊 Secure Dashboard</h2>
        <p>✅ HTTP-Only Cookies - JavaScript cannot access</p>
        <p>✅ SameSite=Strict - CSRF Protection</p>
        <p>✅ Session stored in Database</p>
        <p>✅ Password hashed with bcrypt</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">UNBREAKABLE v1.0</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>